{"tid":463382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港足對巴林友賽前逾20警場外戒備　有球迷噓國歌舉中指大聲叫「去廁所」","createTime":"2017-11-09T12:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T12:23:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"af9e4887ac33e0fd552fed7dbfa2f714d5bfdd9a","tid":463382,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171109/s00001/46cca326fbd3f7cee4f25559c66ed9af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171109%2Fs00001%2F46cca326fbd3f7cee4f25559c66ed9af.jpg&h=412cadb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大常委會早前通過將《國歌法》納入《基本法》附件三中，港府已開展國歌法的本地立法工作，計劃明年向立法會提交立法建議。香港足球代表隊今晚在旺角大球場友賽巴林，賽前有約20多名警員在場外戒備，記者向在場警員查詢，他說「唔方便講」具體任務，稱是正常操作。<br />\n<br />\n大會在球賽開始前播出中國國歌，仍有球迷沒有理會部分港隊球員早前的呼籲，繼續噓國歌，也有球迷大聲叫要「去廁所」離開座位，亦有個別球迷舉中指。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171109/s00001/1510229418351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171109%2Fs00001%2F1510229418351&d=u2V4FAe0VNi%2BBpfrTfl2yE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a5bdca81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171109%2Fs00001%2F1510229418351&h=d6f4908f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171109/s00001/1510229418351</a>"},{"pid":"0bd7efb29591d0e5e018e73d1422becb4e562385","tid":463382,"uid":36178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:20:00.000Z","msg":"噓佢老母！！！"},{"pid":"eedc8929c9ce8da198ae90d9e3b81e416d5451a8","tid":463382,"uid":22858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港支大戰直接嗌屌你老母</span></strong>"},{"pid":"064720780a635b8d346e53caf1d537d364304789","tid":463382,"uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"中國國歌 噓"},{"pid":"da3a4b61a9cefe7d6a3540c429cd31486467a790","tid":463382,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾警犬<br />\n旺角周街死道友唔去巡唔去拉<br />\n做呢d 鷹犬野又咁撚疊碼"}]}